## Quick Reference Table

| Layer | Name         | Key Protocol(s)          | Attack Example          | Cybersecurity Tool     |
|-------|-------------|--------------------------|-------------------------|------------------------|
| 7     | Application  | HTTP, DNS, FTP, SSH      | SQL Injection, XSS      | Burp Suite, OWASP ZAP  |
| 6     | Presentation | TLS/SSL, JPEG, ASCII     | SSL Stripping           | Wireshark, OpenSSL     |
| 5     | Session      | NetBIOS, RPC             | Session Hijacking       | Burp Suite             |
| 4     | Transport    | TCP, UDP                 | SYN Flood, Port Scan    | Nmap, Wireshark        |
| 3     | Network      | IP, ICMP, OSPF           | DDoS, IP Spoofing       | Nmap, Wireshark, ping  |
| 2     | Data Link    | Ethernet, Wi-Fi, ARP     | ARP Spoofing, MAC Flood | Wireshark, arpspoof    |
| 1     | Physical     | Cables, Radio signals    | Wiretapping, Jamming    | Physical inspection    |

